# Thinking in Vim

Vim commands follow a grammar: **verb + modifier + noun** (or **operator + count + motion**)

## The Grammar
  ```
  [count] operator [count] motion/text-object
  ```

  | Component      | Examples                    | Description                    |
  |----------------|-----------------------------|--------------------------------|
  | **Operators**  | `d` `c` `y` `v` `>` `<` `=` | what to do (verb)              |
  | **Motions**    | `w` `e` `b` `j` `k` `$` `0` | where to go                    |
  | **Text Obj**   | `iw` `i"` `ap` `iF`         | what to act on (noun)          |
  | **Count**      | `2` `3` `10`                | how many times                 |

## Common Operators (Verbs)
  | Key | Action                     | Mnemonic        |
  |-----|----------------------------|-----------------|
  | `d` | delete (and yank)          | **d**elete      |
  | `c` | change (delete + insert)   | **c**hange      |
  | `y` | yank (copy)                | **y**ank        |
  | `v` | visual select              | **v**isual      |
  | `>` | indent right               |                 |
  | `<` | indent left                |                 |
  | `=` | auto-format                |                 |
  | `g~`| toggle case                |                 |
  | `gu`| lowercase                  |                 |
  | `gU`| uppercase                  |                 |

## Common Motions (Movement)
  | Key     | Motion                     | Mnemonic        |
  |---------|----------------------------|-----------------|
  | `w`     | start of next word         | **w**ord        |
  | `e`     | end of word                | **e**nd         |
  | `b`     | back to start of word      | **b**ack        |
  | `0`     | start of line              | column **0**    |
  | `$`     | end of line                | regex end       |
  | `^`     | first non-blank            |                 |
  | `gg`    | start of file              | **g**o          |
  | `G`     | end of file                |                 |
  | `f{c}`  | forward to char {c}        | **f**ind        |
  | `t{c}`  | forward until char {c}     | un**t**il       |
  | `F{c}`  | backward to char {c}       |                 |
  | `T{c}`  | backward until char {c}    |                 |
  | `;`     | repeat f/t forward         |                 |
  | `,`     | repeat f/t backward        |                 |
  | `%`     | matching bracket           |                 |
  | `{`     | previous blank line        |                 |
  | `}`     | next blank line            |                 |

## Text Objects (Nouns)
  | Key     | Object                     | Mnemonic        |
  |---------|----------------------------|-----------------|
  | `iw`    | inner word                 | **i**nner       |
  | `aw`    | a word (with spaces)       | **a**round      |
  | `i"`    | inner quotes               |                 |
  | `a"`    | around quotes              |                 |
  | `ip`    | inner paragraph/parens     |                 |
  | `ap`    | around paragraph/parens    |                 |
  | `ib`    | inner block `{}`           | **b**lock       |
  | `ab`    | around block `{}`          |                 |
  | `it`    | inner tag `<>`             | **t**ag         |
  | `at`    | around tag `<>`            |                 |
  | `is`    | inner sentence             | **s**entence    |
  | `iF`    | inner function (mini.ai)   | **F**unction    |

## Delete Patterns
  | Command   | Action                          | Read as                    |
  |-----------|---------------------------------|----------------------------|
  | `x`       | delete char under cursor        | (shortcut for `dl`)        |
  | `dd`      | delete line                     | **d**elete line            |
  | `D`       | delete to end of line           | (shortcut for `d$`)        |
  | `dw`      | delete to next word             | **d**elete **w**ord        |
  | `de`      | delete to end of word           | **d**elete to **e**nd      |
  | `db`      | delete back to word start       | **d**elete **b**ack        |
  | `diw`     | delete inner word               | **d**elete **i**nner **w**ord |
  | `daw`     | delete word + spaces            | **d**elete **a** **w**ord  |
  | `di"`     | delete inside quotes            | **d**elete **i**nside `"`  |
  | `da"`     | delete quotes + content         | **d**elete **a**round `"`  |
  | `dip`     | delete inside parentheses       | **d**elete **i**nner **p**arens |
  | `dib`     | delete inside braces            | **d**elete **i**nner **b**lock |
  | `dit`     | delete inside tag               | **d**elete **i**nner **t**ag |
  | `d$`      | delete to end of line           | **d**elete to `$`          |
  | `d0`      | delete to start of line         | **d**elete to `0`          |
  | `dgg`     | delete to start of file         | **d**elete to **gg**       |
  | `dG`      | delete to end of file           | **d**elete to **G**        |
  | `dt{c}`   | delete until char {c}           | **d**elete un**t**il       |
  | `df{c}`   | delete through char {c}         | **d**elete **f**ind        |
  | `d%`      | delete to matching bracket      | **d**elete to `%`          |
  | `3dd`     | delete 3 lines                  | **3** **d**elete lines     |
  | `d3w`     | delete 3 words                  | **d**elete **3** **w**ords |
  | `diF`     | delete inner function           | **d**elete **i**nner **F**unc |

## Yank (Copy) Patterns
  | Command   | Action                          | Read as                    |
  |-----------|---------------------------------|----------------------------|
  | `yy`      | yank line                       | **y**ank line              |
  | `Y`       | yank to end of line             | (custom, default = `yy`)   |
  | `yw`      | yank to next word               | **y**ank **w**ord          |
  | `yiw`     | yank inner word                 | **y**ank **i**nner **w**ord |
  | `yi"`     | yank inside quotes              | **y**ank **i**nside `"`    |
  | `yip`     | yank inside parentheses         | **y**ank **i**nner **p**arens |
  | `yib`     | yank inside braces              | **y**ank **i**nner **b**lock |
  | `y$`      | yank to end of line             | **y**ank to `$`            |
  | `y0`      | yank to start of line           | **y**ank to `0`            |
  | `yG`      | yank to end of file             | **y**ank to **G**          |
  | `3yy`     | yank 3 lines                    | **3** **y**ank lines       |
  | `yiF`     | yank inner function             | **y**ank **i**nner **F**unc |

## Change Patterns
  | Command   | Action                          | Read as                    |
  |-----------|---------------------------------|----------------------------|
  | `cc`      | change entire line              | **c**hange line            |
  | `C`       | change to end of line           | (shortcut for `c$`)        |
  | `cw`      | change to next word             | **c**hange **w**ord        |
  | `ciw`     | change inner word               | **c**hange **i**nner **w**ord |
  | `ci"`     | change inside quotes            | **c**hange **i**nside `"`  |
  | `ci'`     | change inside single quotes     | **c**hange **i**nside `'`  |
  | `cip`     | change inside parentheses       | **c**hange **i**nner **p**arens |
  | `cib`     | change inside braces            | **c**hange **i**nner **b**lock |
  | `cit`     | change inside tag               | **c**hange **i**nner **t**ag |
  | `ct{c}`   | change until char {c}           | **c**hange un**t**il       |
  | `c$`      | change to end of line           | **c**hange to `$`          |
  | `c0`      | change to start of line         | **c**hange to `0`          |

## Replace Patterns
  | Command   | Action                          | Read as                    |
  |-----------|---------------------------------|----------------------------|
  | `r{c}`    | replace char with {c}           | **r**eplace                |
  | `R`       | enter replace mode              | **R**eplace mode           |
  | `~`       | toggle case of char             |                            |
  | `s`       | substitute char (delete + insert)| **s**ubstitute            |
  | `S`       | substitute line                 | (shortcut for `cc`)        |

## Search Patterns
  | Command         | Action                          |
  |-----------------|---------------------------------|
  | `/pattern`      | search forward                  |
  | `?pattern`      | search backward                 |
  | `n`             | next match                      |
  | `N`             | previous match                  |
  | `*`             | search word under cursor (fwd)  |
  | `#`             | search word under cursor (back) |
  | `gd`            | go to local definition          |
  | `gD`            | go to global definition         |

## Search & Replace Patterns
  | Command                 | Action                                    |
  |-------------------------|-------------------------------------------|
  | `:s/old/new/`           | replace first on line                     |
  | `:s/old/new/g`          | replace all on line                       |
  | `:%s/old/new/g`         | replace all in file                       |
  | `:%s/old/new/gc`        | replace all with confirm                  |
  | `:'<,'>s/old/new/g`     | replace in visual selection               |
  | `:5,10s/old/new/g`      | replace on lines 5-10                     |
  | `:%s/\<word\>/new/g`    | replace exact word only                   |
  | `:%s/old/new/gi`        | replace case insensitive                  |

## Visual Select Patterns
  | Command   | Action                          | Read as                    |
  |-----------|---------------------------------|----------------------------|
  | `viw`     | select inner word               | **v**isual **i**nner **w**ord |
  | `vi"`     | select inside quotes            | **v**isual **i**nside `"`  |
  | `vip`     | select inside parentheses       | **v**isual **i**nner **p**arens |
  | `vib`     | select inside braces            | **v**isual **i**nner **b**lock |
  | `viF`     | select inner function           | **v**isual **i**nner **F**unc |
  | `vap`     | select around parentheses       | **v**isual **a**round **p**arens |
  | `V`       | select line                     | **V**isual line            |
  | `ggVG`    | select entire file              | go top, **V**isual, go end |

## Indent / Format Patterns
  | Command   | Action                          |
  |-----------|---------------------------------|
  | `>>`      | indent line right               |
  | `<<`      | indent line left                |
  | `==`      | auto-format line                |
  | `>ip`     | indent inside paragraph         |
  | `=ip`     | format inside paragraph         |
  | `>iF`     | indent inside function          |
  | `gg=G`    | format entire file              |
  | `3>>`     | indent 3 lines                  |

## Combining with Counts
  | Command   | Action                          |
  |-----------|---------------------------------|
  | `3dw`     | delete 3 words                  |
  | `5dd`     | delete 5 lines                  |
  | `2yy`     | yank 2 lines                    |
  | `3J`      | move down 15 lines (5*3)        |
  | `10j`     | move down 10 lines              |
  | `d3j`     | delete 3 lines down             |
  | `y5k`     | yank 5 lines up                 |
  | `c3w`     | change 3 words                  |
  | `5>>`     | indent 5 lines                  |

## Dot Command (Repeat)
  | Command            | Then `.` repeats              |
  |--------------------|-------------------------------|
  | `ciw` new `<Esc>`  | change word to "new"          |
  | `dd`               | delete line                   |
  | `>>`               | indent line                   |
  | `A;` `<Esc>`       | append semicolon to line      |
  | `daw`              | delete a word                 |

  **Workflow**: Do an edit once, then press `.` to repeat on other locations.
  Use `n` to find next match, `.` to apply same change.

## Common Workflows

  **Change all occurrences of a word:**
  ```
  /word        search for word
  cgn          change next match (auto-selects match)
  new<Esc>     type replacement
  .            repeat on next match
  ```

  **Delete everything inside brackets:**
  ```
  di(          or dip (AZERTY shortcut)
  ```

  **Wrap word in quotes:**
  ```
  saiw"        surround add inner word with "
  ```

  **Change function parameters:**
  ```
  ci(          change inside parentheses
  ```

  **Delete until specific character:**
  ```
  dt,          delete until comma
  df,          delete through comma (includes it)
  ```

  **Copy a function and paste it:**
  ```
  yiF          yank inner function
  p            paste below
  ```

---

# Leader Key
  |                            |                                              |
  |----------------------------|----------------------------------------------|
  | `␣`                        | Leader key                                   |

# Movement (Standard HJKL)
  |                            |                                              |
  |----------------------------|----------------------------------------------|
  | `h`                        | move left                                    |
  | `j`                        | move down                                    |
  | `k`                        | move up                                      |
  | `l`                        | move right                                   |
  |                            |                                              |
  | `H`                        | word backward                                |
  | `J`                        | move down 5 lines                            |
  | `K`                        | move up 5 lines                              |
  | `L`                        | word forward                                 |
  |                            |                                              |
  | `w`                        | move to start of next word                   |
  | `e`                        | move to end of word                          |
  | `b`                        | move to start of previous word               |
  |                            |                                              |
  | `0`                        | start of line                                |
  | `$`                        | end of line                                  |
  | `gg`                       | start of file                                |
  | `G`                        | end of file                                  |

# Insert Mode
  |                            |                                              |
  |----------------------------|----------------------------------------------|
  | `i`                        | enter insert mode                            |
  | `I`                        | insert at beginning of line                  |
  | `a`                        | append after cursor                          |
  | `A`                        | append at end of line                        |
  | `o`                        | open line below                              |
  | `O`                        | open line above                              |
  |                            |                                              |
  | `esc`                      | exit insert mode                             |
  | `jj` / `kk`                | exit insert mode (mini.keymap combo)         |

# Visual Mode
  |                            |                                              |
  |----------------------------|----------------------------------------------|
  | **Entering Visual Mode**   |                                              |
  | `v`                        | visual character mode                        |
  | `V`                        | visual line mode                             |
  | `⌃` `v`                    | visual block mode (column editing!)          |
  | `gv`                       | re-select last visual selection              |
  |                            |                                              |
  | **Movement (HJKL)**        |                                              |
  | `h/j/k/l`                  | extend selection left/down/up/right          |
  | `H/L`                      | extend word back/forward                     |
  | `J/K`                      | extend 5 lines down/up                       |
  | `w/e/b`                    | extend by word                               |
  | `0/$`                      | extend to start/end of line                  |
  | `gg/G`                     | extend to start/end of file                  |
  |                            |                                              |
  | **Operations**             |                                              |
  | `c`                        | change (delete and enter insert)             |
  | `d`                        | delete selection                             |
  | `y`                        | yank (copy) selection                        |
  | `p`                        | paste over selection                         |
  | `u`                        | make lowercase                               |
  | `U`                        | make UPPERCASE                               |
  | `~`                        | toggle case                                  |
  | `<`                        | indent left (keeps selection)                |
  | `>`                        | indent right (keeps selection)               |
  | `o`                        | move to other end of selection               |
  | `:`                        | command mode on selection                    |
  |                            |                                              |
  | **Block Mode (⌃v)**        | rectangular selections                       |
  | `⌃` `v` then `j j j`       | select column down                           |
  | `I` (in block)             | insert at start of block                     |
  | `A` (in block)             | append at end of block                       |
  | `c` (in block)             | change block                                 |
  | `d` (in block)             | delete block                                 |
  |                            |                                              |
  | **Advanced**               |                                              |
  | `V` then `:norm A;`        | add `;` to end of each line                  |
  | `V` then `:norm I//`       | comment each line with `//`                  |
  | `V` then `:s/old/new/g`    | replace in selection only                    |

# File Operations
  |                            |                                              |
  |----------------------------|----------------------------------------------|
  | `␣` `w`                    | save file                                    |
  | `␣` `q`                    | quit                                         |
  | `␣` `x`                    | save and quit                                |
  | `:q`                       | quit (command mode)                          |
  | `:w`                       | save (command mode)                          |

# Fuzzy Finder (Telescope)
  |                            |                                              |
  |----------------------------|----------------------------------------------|
  | `␣` `ff`                   | find files                                   |
  | `␣` `fg`                   | live grep (search in files)                  |
  | `␣` `fb`                   | find buffers                                 |
  | `␣` `fh`                   | find help tags                               |
  | `␣` `fr`                   | recent files                                 |
  | `␣` `fc`                   | git commits                                  |
  | `␣` `fk`                   | find keymaps                                 |
  | `␣` `ft`                   | find theme/colorscheme                       |
  | `␣` `fab`                  | find all buffers (scope)                     |
  |                            |                                              |
  | `⇧` `j`                    | next result (in telescope)                   |
  | `⇧` `k`                    | previous result (in telescope)               |
  | `⏎`                        | select result                                |
  | `esc`                      | close telescope                              |

# Buffer Management
  |                            |                                              |
  |----------------------------|----------------------------------------------|
  | `⌃` `⌥` `l`                | next buffer (hold Caps Lock + l)             |
  | `⌃` `⌥` `h`                | previous buffer (hold Caps Lock + h)         |
  | `⌃` `x` `x`                | delete buffer                                |

# Window/Split Management
  |                            |                                              |
  |----------------------------|----------------------------------------------|
  | `⌃` `w` `v`                | split vertically                             |
  | `⌃` `w` `s`                | split horizontally                           |
  | `⌃` `w` `e`                | equal window sizes                           |
  | `⌃` `w` `t`                | send current window to new tab               |
  | `⌃` `w` `x`                | close current window                         |
  |                            |                                              |
  | `⌃` `w` `h`                | go to left split                             |
  | `⌃` `w` `j`                | go to bottom split                           |
  | `⌃` `w` `k`                | go to upper split                            |
  | `⌃` `w` `l`                | go to right split                            |

# Tab Management
  |                            |                                              |
  |----------------------------|----------------------------------------------|
  | `⌃` `c` `l`                | go to next tab                               |
  | `⌃` `c` `h`                | go to previous tab                           |
  | `⌃` `c` `x`                | close tab                                    |
  | `␣` `tf`                   | new tab with file picker                     |
  |                            |                                              |
  | `␣` `tp`                   | go to previous tab                           |
  | `␣` `tn`                   | go to next tab                               |

# LSP (Language Server)
  |                            |                                              |
  |----------------------------|----------------------------------------------|
  | `gd`                       | go to definition                             |
  | `gr`                       | go to references                             |
  | `gD`                       | go to declaration                            |
  | `gt`                       | go to type definition                        |
  | `gh`                       | hover documentation                          |
  |                            |                                              |
  | `␣` `ca`                   | code action                                  |
  | `␣` `rn`                   | rename symbol                                |
  | `␣` `d`                    | show diagnostics                             |
  |                            |                                              |
  | `[d`                       | previous diagnostic                          |
  | `]d`                       | next diagnostic                              |

# Autocompletion (nvim-cmp)
  |                            |                                              |
  |----------------------------|----------------------------------------------|
  | `⌃` `␣`                    | trigger completion                           |
  | `⏎`                        | confirm selection                            |
  | `⇥`                        | next completion item                         |
  | `⇧` `⇥`                    | previous completion item                     |
  | `⌃` `e`                    | abort completion                             |
  | `⌃` `f`                    | scroll docs forward                          |
  | `⌃` `b`                    | scroll docs backward                         |

# Git
  |                            |                                              |
  |----------------------------|----------------------------------------------|
  | **Lazygit (snacks)**       |                                              |
  | `␣` `gg`                   | open lazygit (root dir)                      |
  | `␣` `gG`                   | open lazygit (cwd)                           |
  | `␣` `gl`                   | lazygit log                                  |
  | `␣` `gf`                   | lazygit file history                         |
  |                            |                                              |
  | **Git Hunks (gitsigns)**   |                                              |
  | `]c`                       | next git hunk                                |
  | `[c`                       | previous git hunk                            |
  | `␣` `gs`                   | stage hunk                                   |
  | `␣` `gr`                   | reset hunk                                   |
  | `␣` `gp`                   | preview hunk                                 |
  | `␣` `gb`                   | blame line                                   |

# Editing
  |                            |                                              |
  |----------------------------|----------------------------------------------|
  | `u`                        | undo                                         |
  | `⌃` `r`                    | redo                                         |
  | `dd`                       | delete line                                  |
  | `yy`                       | yank (copy) line                             |
  | `cc`                       | change line                                  |
  | `p`                        | paste after cursor                           |
  | `P`                        | paste before cursor                          |
  |                            |                                              |
  | **Move Lines (mini.move)** |                                              |
  | `⌥` `h`                    | move selection left                          |
  | `⌥` `j`                    | move line/selection down                     |
  | `⌥` `k`                    | move line/selection up                       |
  | `⌥` `l`                    | move selection right                         |
  |                            |                                              |
  | **Comments**               |                                              |
  | `gcc`                      | toggle comment line                          |
  | `gc` `(motion)`            | comment motion                               |
  | `gb` `(motion)`            | block comment motion                         |

# Surround (mini.surround)
  |                            |                                              |
  |----------------------------|----------------------------------------------|
  | `sa` `(motion)` `(char)`   | add surrounding                              |
  | `sd` `(char)`              | delete surrounding                           |
  | `sr` `(old)` `(new)`       | replace surrounding                          |
  | `sf` `(char)`              | find surrounding (right)                     |
  | `sF` `(char)`              | find surrounding (left)                      |
  | `sh` `(char)`              | highlight surrounding                        |
  |                            |                                              |
  | **Examples**               |                                              |
  | `saiw"`                    | add quotes around word                       |
  | `sa2w)`                    | add parens around 2 words                    |
  | `sd"`                      | delete surrounding quotes                    |
  | `sr"'`                     | replace double with single quotes            |

# Text Objects
  |                            |                                              |
  |----------------------------|----------------------------------------------|
  | **Format**                 | `operator` + `text-object`                   |
  |                            |                                              |
  | **Operators**              |                                              |
  | `d`                        | delete                                       |
  | `c`                        | change (delete + insert mode)                |
  | `y`                        | yank (copy)                                  |
  | `v`                        | visual select                                |
  | `>`                        | indent right                                 |
  | `<`                        | indent left                                  |
  | `=`                        | auto-indent/format                           |
  |                            |                                              |
  | **AZERTY Shortcuts**       | (easier than brackets on AZERTY)             |
  | `ip` / `ap`                | inner/around parentheses `()`                |
  | `ib` / `ab`                | inner/around braces `{}`                     |
  | `ir` / `ar`                | inner/around brackets `[]`                   |
  |                            |                                              |
  | **Standard Objects**       |                                              |
  | `iw` / `aw`                | inner/around word                            |
  | `iW` / `aW`                | inner/around WORD                            |
  | `is` / `as`                | inner/around sentence                        |
  | `i"` / `a"`                | inner/around double quotes                   |
  | `i'` / `a'`                | inner/around single quotes                   |
  | `i(` / `a(`                | inner/around parentheses                     |
  | `i{` / `a{`                | inner/around braces                          |
  | `i[` / `a[`                | inner/around brackets                        |
  | `it` / `at`                | inner/around tag (HTML/XML)                  |
  |                            |                                              |
  | **Mini.ai Extended**       |                                              |
  | `iB` / `aB`                | inner/around buffer                          |
  | `iF` / `aF`                | inner/around function (treesitter)           |
  | `in` / `an`                | inner/around next text object                |
  | `il` / `al`                | inner/around last text object                |
  |                            |                                              |
  | **Examples**               |                                              |
  | `diw`                      | delete inner word                            |
  | `ci"`                      | change inside double quotes                  |
  | `yap`                      | yank around parentheses                      |
  | `dib`                      | delete inside braces                         |
  | `viF`                      | visual select inner function                 |
  | `daF`                      | delete around function                       |

# Search & Replace
  |                            |                                              |
  |----------------------------|----------------------------------------------|
  | `/pattern`                 | search forward                               |
  | `?pattern`                 | search backward                              |
  | `n`                        | next match                                   |
  | `N`                        | previous match                               |
  | `*`                        | search word under cursor forward             |
  | `#`                        | search word under cursor backward            |
  |                            |                                              |
  | `:s/old/new/g`             | replace in line                              |
  | `:%s/old/new/g`            | replace in file                              |
  | `:%s/old/new/gc`           | replace with confirmation                    |

# File Explorer (MiniFiles)
  |                            |                                              |
  |----------------------------|----------------------------------------------|
  | `␣` `ed`                   | open root directory                          |
  | `␣` `eed`                  | open root directory (clean)                  |
  | `␣` `ef`                   | open current file directory                  |
  | `␣` `eef`                  | open last used directory                     |
  |                            |                                              |
  | **In MiniFiles**           |                                              |
  | `h`                        | go out (parent directory)                    |
  | `l`                        | go in (open file/directory)                  |
  | `H`                        | go out and close                             |
  | `L`                        | go in and close                              |
  | `j` / `k`                  | move down/up                                 |
  | `q`                        | close                                        |
  | `=`                        | synchronize changes                          |
  | `@`                        | reveal cwd                                   |

# Session Management (MiniSessions)
  |                            |                                              |
  |----------------------------|----------------------------------------------|
  | `␣` `Sr`                   | restore latest session                       |
  | `␣` `Ss`                   | save session                                 |

# Utility
  |                            |                                              |
  |----------------------------|----------------------------------------------|
  | `␣` `ot`                   | trim all trailing whitespace                 |
  | `␣` `om`                   | toggle minimap                               |

