  | `:checkhealth`             | check neovim health                          |

# Database (vim-dadbod-ui)
  |                            |                                              |
  |----------------------------|----------------------------------------------|
  | `␣` `Do`                   | open database UI in new tab                  |
  | `␣` `Dc`                   | close database tab                           |
  | `␣` `Dt`                   | toggle database drawer                       |
  | `␣` `Df`                   | find database buffer                         |
  | `␣` `Da`                   | add database connection                      |
  |                            |                                              |
  | **In SQL files**           |                                              |
  | `␣` `De`                   | execute query                                |
  |                            |                                              |
  | **In DBUI**                |                                              |
  | `⏎`                        | expand/open item                             |
  | `R`                        | refresh tree                                 |

# Debugging (DAP)
  |                            |                                              |
  |----------------------------|----------------------------------------------|
  | `␣` `db`                   | toggle breakpoint                            |
  | `␣` `dc`                   | continue/start debugging                     |
  | `␣` `di`                   | step into                                    |
  | `␣` `do`                   | step over                                    |
  | `␣` `dO`                   | step out                                     |
  | `␣` `dr`                   | open debug REPL                              |
  | `␣` `dl`                   | run last debug session                       |
  | `␣` `dt`                   | terminate debugging                          |
  | `␣` `du`                   | toggle DAP UI                                |

