# Trouble (Diagnostics)
  |                            |                                              |
  |----------------------------|----------------------------------------------|
  | `␣` `xx`                   | toggle trouble                               |
  | `␣` `xw`                   | workspace diagnostics                        |
  | `␣` `xd`                   | document diagnostics                         |
  | `␣` `xl`                   | location list                                |
  | `␣` `xq`                   | quickfix list                                |

# Tips
- Standard HJKL movement with Shift for fast navigation (H/J/K/L)
- Use `ip`/`ib`/`ir` for easier bracket text objects on AZERTY
- Press `␣?` to see all available keybindings with which-key
- Use `sa`/`sd`/`sr` for surround operations
- Mini.ai extends text objects with `iF`/`aF` for functions, `iB`/`aB` for buffer

